 d(y_k^i,\overline{x})=d(T^{kn}(y_0^i),T^n(\overline{x}))=d((T^n)^k(y_0^i),T^n(\overline{x}))\\=d((\underbrace{T^n\circ\ldots\circ T^n}_{k-\text{times}})(y_0^i),T^n(\overline{x}))\\\leq q~d((T^n)^{k-1}(y_0^i),\overline{x})=q~d((T^n)^{k-1}(y_0^i),T^n(\overline{x}))\\\leq q^2~d((T^n)^{k-2}(y_0^i),\overline{x})\leq\ldots\\\leq q^k~d(y_0^i,\overline{x}). 
